    "In the next subsection, I will motivate this premise.",
    "P1 states that future AI may have more advanced capacities which suffice for being able to disempower humanity.",
    "To establish P1, it is not only necessary to show that humanity is capable of building sufficiently capable AI, but also that this is feasible by 2100.",
    "To motivate this claim, let us look first at the capacities AI might plausibly need to disempower humanity.",
    "Traditionally, worries about human disempowerment through AI have often focused on so-called 'superintelligence' (Bostrom 2014)."
